YoY Avg Price 14

1.Right Click on YoY Sales  and select Duplicate. Change the name of the sheet to YOY Avg Price. Remove all the fields from the marks shelf.



2. Drag and drop Text under Marks

<AGG(_YOY Avg price % )>

<AGG(cc.Mark AvgPrice KPI Indicator UP)>

<AGG(cc.Mark AvgPrice KPI Indicator Down)>





3. Right click on YOY Avg Price under marks shelf and select format > Pane > Numbers Custom > Percentage > Decimal places 2





4. Click on Text select the ellipses (…) and Highlight all the text select Tableau Bold. Select Font size 12 and Font type Bold. Click on the Alignment and select Horizontal Center and Vertical Center




5. Click on the Text and select    <AGG(_YOY Avg price % )> and change the color to Yellow #edc948 . Likewise select <AGG(cc.Mark AvgPrice KPI Indicator UP)> and change the color to Green (  #59a14f ) and select  <AGG(cc.Mark AvgPrice KPI Indicator Down)> and change the color to Red (#e15759). Arrange in one line Click Ok.








6.Rt Click on the tile and select Edit title and select the title Tableau Semi bold> font size 10 > font type bold > Color Black >Alignment as Center.
